  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Eve Williams And The Secret Of The Trunk?</h2><br><strong>Eve Williams And The Secret Of The Trunk</strong> is the creation of a solo developer from Germany and a game that blurs the lines between a classic point-and-click adventure and a decision-driven visual novel.<br><br>In the fictional city of New Cologne, you'll step into the shoes of Eve, a tough-as-nails private detective whose skill and choices will determine your path through this dark and captivating story. <strong>Eve Williams And The Secret Of The Trunk</strong> offers you the unique opportunity to dive into a world where every decision counts and every interaction can influence your fate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/e16b4a9645dc35e7ec1f943530f484dd.poster.avif?t=1712056449\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/e16b4a9645dc35e7ec1f943530f484dd.webm?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/e16b4a9645dc35e7ec1f943530f484dd.mp4?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>Exploration and Interaction:</strong> Dive into Eve's world, explore her surroundings, and solve complex puzzles by skillfully combining items in your inventory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/8e5bac1bfc6137c3418484612974fc0b.poster.avif?t=1712056449\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/8e5bac1bfc6137c3418484612974fc0b.webm?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/8e5bac1bfc6137c3418484612974fc0b.mp4?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Communication as a Tool:</strong> Use your communication skills to gather information, build relationships, and advance the story. The way you interact can shed light on the mysteries or lead to unexpected turns.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/520f766aca555b0178051e7c723a547e.poster.avif?t=1712056449\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/520f766aca555b0178051e7c723a547e.webm?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/520f766aca555b0178051e7c723a547e.mp4?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Inclusive Narrative:</strong> As an LGBTQ+-friendly game, we embrace diversity and offer an inclusive experience that respects and celebrates the diversity of identities and relationships.<br><br><strong>Classic Look Meets Modern Narrative:</strong> Enjoy the perfect blend of classic point-and-click adventure design and the expressive, profound dialogues of a visual novel.<br><br><strong>Action-Packed Moments:</strong> Quick Time Events inject dynamism and excitement into the story, challenging your reflexes and providing a varied gaming experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/1286523b9c5f5818a6bc1f5b10f587ff.poster.avif?t=1712056449\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/1286523b9c5f5818a6bc1f5b10f587ff.webm?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/1286523b9c5f5818a6bc1f5b10f587ff.mp4?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Often there is more than one way to the goal.</strong> However, it does matter which one you choose. Eve Williams And The Secret Of The Trunk comes with several different endings– every choice matters and can steer the story in a completely new direction.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/1e3e50d20caf31961eeb19f76b3d3fec.poster.avif?t=1712056449\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/1e3e50d20caf31961eeb19f76b3d3fec.webm?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939130/extras/1e3e50d20caf31961eeb19f76b3d3fec.mp4?t=1712056449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
